![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/1578167546870-376WNQ4WAEXXL1T602NK/image-asset.jpeg)

On this episode of Major Issues, the guys gush over the classic Frank Miller/Daredevil story Daredevil: Born Again. Full of action, betrayal, blood, and drugs, this epic story deals with what would happen if Daredevil's greatest foe found out his secret identity! This story zigs everywhere you think it'll zag and will keep you on the egde of your seat, epsecially when you remember it was written over 30 years ago. Come for the story and stay for the discussion as the guys try to decide where its staying power truly lies!

If you can, please leave us a **_review_** on [**ITunes**](https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/major-issues-podcast/id1321720972) so we can grow our audience and grow as podcasters! Rate us where ever podcasts are found. Don't forget to check out our merchandise! All episodes of Major Issues are brought to you by **ComicBook Clique**, the one stop for the latest and greatest things to come to comic books and comic book media.  
  
